      <title>特鲁多表示不会在预算中对中产阶级增税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trudeau-says-he-won-t-raise-taxes-on-middle-class-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，加拿大即将出台的预算不会包括对中产阶级征收新税，但没有评论政府是否会采取其他措施来增加税收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trudeau-says-he-won-t-raise-taxes-on-middle-class-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:42:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登的顾问敦促亚马逊和家得宝保留巴尔的摩的就业机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/biden-team-urges-amazon-home-depot-to-keep-baltimore-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的顾问已致电巴尔的摩的主要雇主——包括 Amazon.com Inc. 和 Home Depot Inc. –据知情人士透露，尽管桥梁倒塌导致该市港口关闭，但仍鼓励他们保住工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/biden-team-urges-amazon-home-depot-to-keep-baltimore-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁国会拒绝就劳力士丑闻弹劾博卢阿特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/peru-s-congress-rejects-impeaching-boluarte-over-rolex-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁国会周四驳回了针对不受欢迎的总统迪娜·博卢阿特 (Dina Boluarte) 的两项弹劾动议，后者正在就非法致富和使用劳力士手表的政治丑闻展开刑事调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/peru-s-congress-rejects-impeaching-boluarte-over-rolex-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦当劳将购买成为哈马斯战争爆发点的以色列特许经营权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mcdonald-s-mcd-to-buy-israel-franchise-that-became-flashpoint-in-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦当劳公司同意从运营商 Alonyal Ltd. 手中收购其在以色列的餐厅，将这家当地连锁店纳入公司内部。几个月前，该连锁店在以色列与哈马斯战争初期成为争议焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mcdonald-s-mcd-to-buy-israel-franchise-that-became-flashpoint-in-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:58:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市拥堵费之争威胁 MTA 在债务成本方面取得的进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/congestion-pricing-fight-risks-mta-s-progress-on-debt-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约大都会交通管理局拥堵收费计划面临的法律挑战可能会导致该机构控制借贷成本的成功化为泡影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/congestion-pricing-fight-risks-mta-s-progress-on-debt-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多为非营利组织设立基金购买公寓楼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trudeau-creates-fund-for-nonprofits-to-buy-apartment-buildings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多总理的政府正在制定一项 15 亿加元（合 11 亿美元）的计划，帮助加拿大非营利组织购买经济适用公寓楼并降低租金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trudeau-creates-fund-for-nonprofits-to-buy-apartment-buildings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:19:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
